Thanks to their ongoing touring and top-selling catalog titles, Maze featuring Frankie Beverly remain one of the most popular R&B groups of all time! Enjoy one of their best live performances, culled from their 12 show dates at New Orleans Saenger Theatre (and from the companion gold-selling album).
